<ElliciumText TextStyle="TextStyle.Subtitle1" TagName="TagName.P" class="rz-pb-4">
    <strong>ElliciumLayout</strong> allows you to define the global layout of your application (usually used in MainLayout.razor).
    It has header, sidebar, body and footer sections which correspond to the <code>ElliciumHeader</code>, <code>ElliciumSidebar</code>, <code>ElliciumBody</code> and <code>ElliciumFooter</code> components.
    Sections are optional and can be omitted.
</ElliciumText>

